div.dash-page
  .section.intro-section
      h1 Our Movements
      p.
        We started in 2009 as a small project. We have been importing finished furniture from European countries like Germany, Denmark. We also import our finished furniture in neighboring countries like Kenya, Burundi. Local customers are among our interests. Furniture is stocked and together with our stable suppliers from around Uganda. For this reason we are the potential company to design your office, home, dining halls, hotels etc.

      h3.mb-0 some of our details
      pre.mt-0.mb-2.
        Mayondo Wood and Furniture (MWF) Ltd operates under a registered license Board. 
        The top selling products are the office furniture, beds and cupboards.

